<Button variant="outline" className="border-zinc-800 text-foreground hover:bg-zinc-800">
  Outline Button
</Button>
```

**CRITICAL TEXT COLOR RULES**:

- **On zinc backgrounds** (zinc-950, zinc-800): Always use `text-foreground` (light) or `text-muted-foreground` (muted light). Never use dark text.
- **On lime/accent backgrounds** (`bg-accent`): Always use `text-accent-foreground` (dark `#000000`). NEVER use white or light text.

